Title: Mei Mei
Writer: Joe Gayton (created by), Tony Gayton (created by), John Wirth, Tom Brady, Max Hurwitz (staff writer), Miki Johnson (staff writer)
Actors: Anson Mount, Christopher Heyerdahl, Tim Guinee, Byron Mann
Plot: Cullen enlists new workers to help him move a locomotive on a sled; Cullen and Fong must work together; Swede and Phineas fight for survival after being banished to the high country.
